verbose_text: Additionally, after DGKalpha genes were transferred into HB8521 cells, lower levels of cell proliferation and IL-2 expression were observed in response to immune stimulation in cells transfected with the targeted polyplexes than in cells that had n't been pre-transfected during stimulation, demonstrating that MRI-visible targeted nanoparticles can dampen TCR induced diacylglycerol signaling.
